32:11 GMT</span><br><div class="category"><strong>Category: </strong><span class="category-text">world</span></div><br><div class="source"><strong>Source: </strong><span class="source-text">The Guardian</span></div><br><div class="link"><a href="https://www.theguardian.com/politics/2023/aug/08/left-in-limbo-by-brexit-safety-mark-chaos" target="_blank">Click here to read the full article</a></div><br></div><hr><div class='item'><h2><a href="https://www.theguardian.com/football/2023/aug/08/colombia-will-approach-england-like-germany-says-coach-abadia" target="_blank">Colombia turn focus to England as Lauren James issues red-card apology</a></h2><div class="description"> Nelson Abadía: ‘We will face England with composure’ Colombia face England in a World Cup quarter-final on Saturday. Colombia beat Jamaica 1-0 to reach the last eight for the first time in their World Cup history. Colombia will draw on approach that they used to stun Germany in their last 16 win over the Germans.</div><br><span class="date"><strong>Published on:</strong> Tue, 08 Aug 2023 15:31:43 GMT</span><br><div class="category"><strong>Category: </strong><span class="category-text">world</span></div><br><div class="source"><strong>Source: </strong><span class="source-text">The Guardian</span></div><br><div class="link"><a href="https://www.theguardian.com/football/2023/aug/08/colombia-will-approach-england-like-germany-says-coach-abadia" target="_blank">Click here to read the full article</a></div><br></div><hr><div class='item'><h2><a href="https://www.theguardian.com/football/2023/aug/08/le-sommer-fires-france-past-morocco-to-set-up-australia-quarter-final" target="_blank">Le Sommer fires France past Morocco to set up Australia quarter-final</a></h2><div class="description"> Aussies face France in World Cup quarter-final against co-hosts in Brisbane on Saturday morning. The game promises to be one of the defining games of this tournament, a tantalising collision of Aussie guts and French guile. T