w the USWNT can improve for 2027</a></h2><div class="description"> USA's exit in the last-16 marked their worst finish ever at a major tournament. There are many issues to address within the US soccer ecosystem. There is also an Olympics in less than a year, and work to be done on the field immediately. Here’s a to-do list for the powers that be.</div><br><span class="date"><strong>Published on:</strong> Tue, 08 Aug 2023 15:25:22 GMT</span><br><div class="category"><strong>Category: </strong><span class="category-text">entertainment</span></div><br><div class="source"><strong>Source: </strong><span class="source-text">The Guardian</span></div><br><div class="link"><a href="https://www.theguardian.com/football/2023/aug/08/identity-and-overseas-experience-how-the-uswnt-can-improve-for-2027" target="_blank">Click here to read the full article</a></div><br></div><hr><div class='item'><h2><a href="https://www.theguardian.com/football/2023/aug/09/premier-league-2023-24-preview-no-15-newcastle-united" target="_blank">Premier League 2023-24 preview No 15: Newcastle United</a></h2><div class="description"> Eddie Howe's side have Champions League football to look forward to, but might domestic form take a hit as a result? The Howe side are currently 6th in the Premier League table, according to the average of our writers’ predictions for this season’s position.</div><br><span class="date"><strong>Published on:</strong> Tue, 08 Aug 2023 23:01:40 GMT</span><br><div class="category"><strong>Category: </strong><span class="category-text">sports</span></div><br><div class="source"><strong>Source: </strong><span class="source-text">The Guardian</span></div><br><div class="link"><a href="https://www.theguardian.com/football/2023/aug/09/premier-league-2023-24-preview-no-15-newcastle-united" target="_blank">Click here to read the full article</a></div><br></div><hr><div class='item'><h2><a href="https://www.theguardian.com/football/2023/aug/08/wolves-gary-oneil-manager-julen-lopetegui